    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>anibus</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>Val</abbr><ex>erius</ex></expan> Felix princeps offi<lb break="no" n="3"/><expan><abbr>ci</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan> pr<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>esidis</abbr></expan> vixit <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>nos</ex></expan> XLV <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>Aurel</abbr><ex>ia</ex></expan> Aemilia bene meri<lb break="no" n="5"/>to conpari <note>sic</note> virginio posuit <lb n="6"/>vale viator </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Οὐαλ(έριος) Φήλιξ πρίνκιψ ὀφηκίου <surplus>ὀφικίου</surplus> <lb n="2"/>ἡγεμόνος ζήσας ἔτη μεʹ <lb n="3"/>Αὐρελ(ία) Ἐμιλία τῷ ἀειμνήστῳ <lb n="4"/>ἀνδρὶ παρθενικῷ τὴν στήλην ἀν<supplied reason="lost">έ</supplied><lb break="no" n="5"/>θηκεν· χαῖρε παροδεῖτα
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Obere rechte Hälfte erhalten; oberhalb des Inschriftfeldes eine männliche Büste. Z. 2 (Ende): statt F auch E möglich. (B): AE 1939: Z. 5 nicht angegeben.</p>
